   <text type="letter">
      <body>
         
            <opener>
               
               <salute>Dear Walt.&#8212;</salute>
            </opener>
         <p>What the devil is the matter? Nothing serious I<ptr target="loc.00572_n100"/> hope.&#8212;It seems mighty queer that I cannot succeed in having one word from you.&#8212;I swear I would have thought you would be the last man in this world to neglect me.&#8212;But I am afraid.&#8212;</p>
            <p>Lizzie is married!, Johnny is dead! Walt has forgotten.</p>
            <closer rend="right">
               <salute>Such is life, Yours,</salute>
               <signed>Fred.</signed>
            </closer>
         
      </body>
